wifts-1989-taylors-version-breaks-two-spotify-records-3525033">该唱片在登陆Spotify平台后不久也打破了该平台的新纪录</a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">一篇五星级评论</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>称赞这位流行歌星最近的重新录制是“不可否认的令人着迷的练习”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-reveals-which-taylor-swift-song-deeply-impacted-him-3561348">杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff) 透露泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的哪首歌对他影响深远，这篇文章</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
